parameters.name: TableId
parameters.description: The ID of the logical table. You can call the [ListLogicTables](https://www.alibabacloud.com/help/en/data-management-service/latest/listlogictables) operation to query the ID of the logical table.

parameters.name: Tid
parameters.description: The ID of the tenant. You can call the [GetUserActiveTenant](https://www.alibabacloud.com/help/en/data-management-service/latest/getuseractivetenant) operation to query the tenant ID.
